impactEvaluationDescription:
I implemented the W.A.G.M.I. protocol:

We all know that RetroPGF is a great idea, and we're still trying to come up with a good way to measure the gap. We're also confident that it will happen eventually. And yes, we know that there's been a lot of chance in this round. We're getting there. Well-known projects are getting rewarded appropriately, but less known projects have low visibility. We might as well consider what few are signaling and give these projects one little final push to an opportunity.
